        <h2  >修炎真吾的影评 &nbsp; &middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
        <span class="pl">( <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/rocchow/reviews?cat_id=1002">18篇</a> )</span></h2>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
            <div class="pic">
                <a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/3821067/" title="一代宗師"><img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s24591423.jpg" alt="一代宗師"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>
                    <a title="《一代宗师》：不如将错就错，喝下这杯苦咖啡" href="http://movie.douban.com/review/5738434/" class="title">《一代宗师》：不如将错就错，喝下这杯苦咖啡</a>
                </h3>
                <div class="author">
